reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to assemble!
reviews.reviewText: It was very easy to assemble. It’s pretty sturdy, perfect size for what I needed it for.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well Built. Easy Assembly. Looks Great!
reviews.reviewText: Very simple to put together. All components fit perfectly together with no issues.I love that it has an outlet hidden in the back decently out of sight.The barn style cabinet door really boosts the asthetics, and matches my barn style Tv Stand almost exactly.It also came with a medium/full size screwdriver which is much easier to use than the mini ones normally supplied with other products. Plus its nice to keep around the house for future use.Overall great product. Fairly priced. Would recommend. We shall see how it lasts, but it does seem very sturdy with no weak connections between pieces.Only critique would be that the cabinet door slightly bends when opening due to the super strong magnet holding it shut. But nothing too concerning as it holds its shape. Maybe the magnet should have been desgined to lay behind where the knob is instead of on the top of the cabinet, for smoother functioning.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These end tables were a great bang for the buck. Upsides: they are cute, easy to assemble, convenient. Downsides: they are a bit small and the charger port sometimes makes a high frequency noise when things are plugged in.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to join up
reviews.reviewText: Is a good nigth table, was easy to put all together( 35min in average) and the quality is according to the price.Happy with this purchase.PD. You don’t need extra tools, all is inside the box.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy end tables at a good price point
reviews.reviewText: I bought 2 of these end tables for my living room.The packaging was very good, all of the pieces were clearly labeled which made for easy assembly.I was actually a little surprised by how solid the wood pieces are, which really made me happy about my purchase.They look good and will serve us well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Price could be lower for this small piece of furniture with easy directions
reviews.reviewText: Screws were all silver and not white as in the advertisement. I feel that makes it look cheap. Everything lined up well when in correct direction. Took me an hour to put together because the pre drilled holes did not accept the screws well. It is small and serves the purpose for the guest room. Power cord is a great addition. I have put many different pieces of furniture together this was more difficult to crew together. Has the feel of cube storage with a door.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. this is the easiest and cutest nightstand!! i highly recommend it!! i also love the compartment it is enough room to fit so many things but also isn’t a drawer so reduces clutter. I love love love it!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars DO NOT WASTE YOUR MONEY
reviews.reviewText: Shipping was terrible, product is horrendously cheap, assembly and instructions were so bad. Like many other reviews says that’s are tiny, they look like doll furniture. I’ve put together a bunch of “ikea” type furniture and this was by far the worst. Materials couldn’t be cheaper. Save your money and get something usable. These will not be staying in my bedroom
